## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-102"><xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute>屬性會指定表單欄位驗證時，欄位必須包含值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-102">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute> attribute specifies that when a field on a form is validated, the field must contain a value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-103">如果屬性是，驗證例外狀況會引發`null`，包含空字串 ("")，或只包含空格字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-103">A validation exception is raised if the property is `null`, contains an empty string (""), or contains only white-space characters.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-104">如果 MVC 資料模型或實體部分類別包含的欄位，將附註<xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute>屬性，但頁面不包含屬性，則不會引發錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-104">If the MVC data model or entity partial class contains a field that is annotated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute> attribute, but the page does not contain the property, an error is not raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-105">只針對提交給伺服器的欄位，進行驗證。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-105">Validation occurs only for fields that are submitted to the server.</span></span>  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-106">下列範例會使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute>覆寫允許資料欄位是空的資料庫結構描述規則的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-106">The following example uses the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute> attribute to override the database schema rule that allows a data field to be empty.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-107">此範例會執行下列步驟：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-107">The example performs the following steps:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-108">會實作中繼資料的部分類別和相關聯的中繼資料類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-108">Implements a metadata partial class and the associated metadata class.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-109">在相關聯的中繼資料類別中，它會套用<xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute>屬性會指定下列需求：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-109">In the associated metadata class, it applies the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.RequiredAttribute> attribute, which specifies the following requirements:</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-110">[標題] 資料欄位不可空白。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-110">The Title data field cannot be empty.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-111">如果驗證失敗，此範例中的程式碼會擲回驗證例外狀況，並顯示錯誤訊息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-111">If validation fails, the code in the example throws a validation exception and displays an error message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-112">在指定的錯誤訊息時，屬性會套用至資料欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-112">The error message is specified at the time that the attribute is applied to the data field.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-113">MiddleName 資料欄位不可空白。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-113">The MiddleName data field cannot be empty.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="db9a5-114">如果驗證失敗，此範例中的程式碼會擲回驗證例外狀況，並顯示錯誤訊息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db9a5-114">If validation fails, the code in the example throws a validation exception and displays an error message.</span></span>  
  
